## 🧑‍💻 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

* Node.js
* Java 17+
* Python 3.x
* MySQL
* Redis
* Kafka

---

### Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo.git
cd your-repo
```

---

### Backend

```bash
cd backend
./mvnw spring-boot:run
```

---

### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

---

### AI Service

```bash
cd ml-service
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

